Believe:TheStoryOfOlympicTaekwondoAthlet.name: Believe: The Story of Olympic Taekwondo Athlete Victoria Stambaugh - Black Belt Exclusive
Believe:TheStoryOfOlympicTaekwondoAthlet.summary: Believe: The Story of Olympic Taekwondo Athlete Victoria Stambaugh - Black Belt Exclusive. Victoria Stambaugh's journey to the Olympics has seen no shortage of challenges and detours. From dealing with multiple career-ending injuries, to standing up after crushing losses, she has shown that her steadfast faith, grace in defeat, and strength to push forward has helped her finally find what it takes to make it to the biggest and most prestigious sports tournament in the world.

ChonJi-ABentonMartialArtsDocumentary.name: Chon Ji - A Benton Martial Arts Documentary
ChonJi-ABentonMartialArtsDocumentary.summary: This is a film which depicts the martial arts journey of siblings Madeline and Aidan Fulgium from the origin of their Dojang to their experience in international competition in ITF Taekwondo.
